===Travelers Rest connector===

U.S. Route 276 Connector (US 276 Conn.) is a connector route, in concurrency with US 25 Conn., along Poinsett Highway. It connects US 276 with US 25, in downtown Travelers Rest. Not only is the highway unsigned, it is not even shown on SCDOT&#x27;s Greenville metro area map, so the highway may be decommissioned.
